Content: Pro traders arent any better at predicting where the market will go than a hobby trader and its not the job. The difference is all in execution Finding lvls protecting profits once available stopping out  adjusting when wrong and consistant loss size control. Focus there

After nearly 24hrs of relentless rally and 130 points from the 5438 long trigger #ES_F finally seeing its first dip. 5560 was support as posted and after trying for 30mins to bounce it cracked. 544237 was 1st target down just hit.   5528 5519 below. Must reclaim 60 to pop

We are up a staggering 170 points from yesterdays low  and 130 points from yesterdays 5438 long trigger with no dip. ES finally putting in a micro dip attempt. 5560support as posted this was my upside target yesterday now backtesting.  Bulls must push fast. Sell 554337 below

Yesterday was the most impressive short squeeze of 2024 in #ES_F. 5438 reclaim was long trigger provided. 5519 hit 5528 hit 5560 hit were target. Nothing to do but trail stops until we dip.  Plan 5560support. Keeps 558593 major 5605 live. 5560 fails dip 554337

Closing update #ES_F Another CPI day done and as warned last night it would be volatile. We are 100 points from the 5438 long trigger. Hold runners. Bulls want to hold 551922 on any dips to keep 5560 5585 live. Newsletter out soon talking triggers tradecompanion.substack.com

Runners continue to print money and we are now an incredible 107 points from todays long trigger off the reclaim of 5438 as we see the power of the Failed Breakdownbear trap. I gave the following targets 5519 hit 5528 hit 5560.   Just keep trailing up those stops

And there is officially 100 points from todays 5438 long trigger in #ES_F. We can see here the power of failed breakdowns and bear traps and why we need to trade after the traps. Just keep riding those longs now and dragging the stops up.  5519 hit 5528 hit 5560 next

Theres 5519 next target up hit and now up 80 points from the 5438 long trigger after a classic bear trapfailed breakdown in #ES_F. Obviously after 80 points anymore is bonus today. Just let runners as we continue this leg.  5528 5560 next up if ES wants it. 5491support

We are now up 73 points from the 5438 long trigger provided. Ride those runners  While some may be surprised by todays action it is  routine. As warned in last nights newsletter CPI dayand  lesser extent everyday in #ES_F is about traps. Our goal is to trade after the traps

Incredible follow through in #ES_F 5414 was support as posted with 5438 needed to trigger longs again. We held 5414 recovered 5438 and now 54 points. Lots of vol to go nowhere  Arriving at 5491 next trgt. Protect your gains now hold runners. 5502 5519 next. 5474support

Typical CPI trapping continues in #ES_F. This is what CPI days look like  its a dream market for lvl to lvl traders. 5414 was support as posted with 5438 reclaim needed to trigger long. We held 14 reclaim 5438 squeezed.  5474 is next res must recover to bottom. 5438support

5414 next level down just hit in #ES_F as we continue the CPI day volatility. 5473 has been the key pivot. It triggered longs on the 1st testfailed breakdown after CPI then shorts on its failure at 10am.  Bears control until a resistance reclaims 5438. 5404 5393 below

CPI continuing to deliver typical volatility in #ES_F  5473 has been key pivot. Its failed breakdown on 1st test triggered long to 5505. I posted after that 5473 fail triggers dip to 5458 5438  we are working down lvls nicely  5414 5404 next down. 5438 must recover to pop

Very routine CPI action continues in #ES_F and weve had several great level to level moves. 5473 was support as posted with 5473 flush and recover being long trigger. We got to 5505. Now flushing again for 2nd time  No change 5458 5438 below. 5473 must recover to trigger up

As provided in last nights newsletter what we saw after CPI was typical. #ES_F traps by its nature. We flushed to 5471 support took out overnight low recovered triggered long. Now protect gains trapping not done  5482 5473 sell belowsupports. 5511 5519 5528 upside

Very typical CPI reaction today with the 1st move trap. As posted at 8am 5473 was must hold for bulls. We sold there held itflushed slightly then rallied now 30 points. Lock in gains let a risk free runner go all bonus.   5511 5518 5528 if #ES_F wants. 5491support

Initial CPI reaction in the books for #ES_F and usual 1st move is a trap. 5473 support as posted and we dipped there flushed itthe overnight low slightly bounced 15 points. As always with CPI No greed with profits.  5491 must recover to rally 5519. 73 fails dip 5838

Yesterday was consolidation day as we await CPI in #ES_F. 5474 reclaim was long trigger as posted with 5492 5502 targets and we got it yesterday backtested 5474 again last night  Plan today Size down. Bulls want to hold 5482 5473 to keep 5502 5518 live. 74 fails dip 58 38

Closing update #ES_F Right at 5502 as we head into the close and head into CPI. Relief rally remains in tact 5511 5519 5528 if bulls want it from here. 5482support and we work back down the lvls below. Newsletter out soon talking plan tomorrow tradecompanion.substack.com
